"{\"uid\": \"russian-sports.ru-en-will-russia-go-to-the-olympics.html\", \"entities\": [{\"sentence\": \"Take part in the mass poll \\\"Will Russia go to the Olympics?\", \"from\": 0, \"to\": 59, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 33, \"end\": 39, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8868656385948841, \"rank\": 0.12235937739030044, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\".You can vote until July 1, 2024 and you can do it once from one internet device.\", \"from\": 59, \"to\": 141, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"There is not much time left before the start of the2024 Olympics, but the debate in the sports community is not subsiding.\", \"from\": 143, \"to\": 265, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Some believe that Russia should participate in the Games, while others express the opposite opinion: \\\"participation of our national team under discriminatory conditions is unacceptable.\", \"from\": 266, \"to\": 451, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 284, \"end\": 290, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8868656385948841, \"rank\": 0.12235937739030044, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Each sports federation in our country has its own opinion.\", \"from\": 453, \"to\": 511, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"For example, Russian rowers refused to take part in the qualifying competitions and, consequently, refused to participate in the Olympics.\", \"from\": 512, \"to\": 650, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 525, \"end\": 532, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9999999891513199, \"rank\": 1.0716763672115035e-08, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On the contrary, the Russian Tennis Federation (FTR) is proud of the achievements of Russian athletes and supports their participation in major international competitions.\", \"from\": 651, \"to\": 822, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 672, \"end\": 697, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Tennis_Federation\", \"score\": 0.9999590305144826, \"rank\": 4.0971164143629466e-05, \"text\": \"Russian Tennis Federation\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Tennis_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_Tennis_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 699, \"end\": 702, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FTR_Moto\", \"score\": 0.9999994871654003, \"rank\": 5.128286048063801e-07, \"text\": \"FTR\", \"types\": [\"Q4830453\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FTR_Moto\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/FTR_Moto\"}, {\"begin\": 736, \"end\": 743, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9999999891513199, \"rank\": 1.0716763672115035e-08, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Recall, the IOC announced the criteria for Russian and Belarusian athletes to be admitted to the Games back in December 2023.\", \"from\": 824, \"to\": 949, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 836, \"end\": 839, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 2.2086178285634946e-22, \"text\": \"IOC\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Olympic_Committee\"}, {\"begin\": 867, \"end\": 874, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"score\": 0.9999999891513199, \"rank\": 1.0716763672115035e-08, \"text\": \"Russian\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russian_language\"}, {\"begin\": 879, \"end\": 889, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9996672615351666, \"rank\": 0.00031034698514177195, \"text\": \"Belarusian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Athletes will perform under a neutral flag and will not be admitted to the parade of athletes at the opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 950, \"to\": 1068, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In team events, athletes will not perform at all.\", \"from\": 1070, \"to\": 1119, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Nor will those who support the SMO, including support staff.\", \"from\": 1120, \"to\": 1180, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1151, \"end\": 1154, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smoothened\", \"score\": 0.9082245140281362, \"rank\": 0.10104933745610556, \"text\": \"SMO\", \"types\": [\"Q7187\", \"Q206229\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smoothened\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smoothened\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"All paraphernalia, symbols of Russia and Belarus (anthem, flag, national colors, etc.)\", \"from\": 1181, \"to\": 1267, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1211, \"end\": 1217, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8868656385948841, \"rank\": 0.12235937739030044, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}, {\"begin\": 1222, \"end\": 1229, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"score\": 0.9992027962850275, \"rank\": 0.0007967833111653475, \"text\": \"Belarus\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Belarus\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"will not and should not be displayed at the games.\", \"from\": 1268, \"to\": 1318, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Coaches and sports officials will also not be allowed to participate and only a doctor or technical staff will be able to assist the athlete.\", \"from\": 1319, \"to\": 1460, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"In addition, athletes must avoid interviews during and after the Olympics on the topic of national committees, national symbols, the SMO and everything related to it.\", \"from\": 1462, \"to\": 1628, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1595, \"end\": 1598, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smoothened\", \"score\": 0.9082245140281362, \"rank\": 0.10104933745610556, \"text\": \"SMO\", \"types\": [\"Q7187\", \"Q206229\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smoothened\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Smoothened\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The Ukrainian Olympic Committee additionally requires that all athletes sign a waiver to participate in the2024 World Friendship Games.\", \"from\": 1629, \"to\": 1764, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1633, \"end\": 1642, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"score\": 0.9056632360787055, \"rank\": 0.09534725319782318, \"text\": \"Ukrainian\", \"types\": [\"Q315\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Ukrainian_language\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In connection with the ambiguous opinion of athletes and their coaches, we want to ask you, dear readers, are you ready to see Russia at the Olympics 2024 under a neutral flag?\", \"from\": 1766, \"to\": 1942, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1893, \"end\": 1899, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"score\": 0.8868656385948841, \"rank\": 0.12235937739030044, \"text\": \"Russia\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Russia\"}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Should we go to it at all?\", \"from\": 1943, \"to\": 1969, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"We think that your opinion will be able to influence the decision of those athletes who are still undecided.\", \"from\": 1970, \"to\": 2078, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u041f\\u0440\\u043e\\u0433\\u043e\\u043b\\u043e\\u0441\\u043e\\u0432\\u0430\\u0442\\u044c \\u043c\\u043e\\u0436\\u043d\\u043e 1 \\u0440\\u0430\\u0437 \\u0441 \\u043e\\u0434\\u043d\\u043e\\u0433\\u043e \\u0438\\u043d\\u0442\\u0435\\u0440\\u043d\\u0435\\u0442 \\u0443\\u0441\\u0442\\u0440\\u043e\\u0439\\u0441\\u0442\\u0432\\u0430.\", \"from\": 2080, \"to\": 2135, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"\\u0414\\u043e\\u043f\\u0443\\u0441\\u0442\\u0438\\u043c\\u043e \\u0432\\u044b\\u0431\\u0438\\u0440\\u0430\\u0442\\u044c \\u0434\\u043e 3-\\u0445 \\u0432\\u0430\\u0440\\u0438\\u0430\\u043d\\u0442\\u043e\\u0432 / You can vote once from one internet device.\", \"from\": 2136, \"to\": 2217, \"entities\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Up to 3 options can be selected.\", \"from\": 2218, \"to\": 2250, \"entities\": []}]}"